<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5726544>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–12. 7–10) Callichroma sp., male identified by Schmidt as C. carinatum (ZMHB): 7) Dorsal habitus, including entire antennae; 8) Dorsal habitus; 9) Head and pronotum; 10) Labels. 11) Callichroma chiriquina, lectotype male, dorsal habitus (By Jesus Santiago Moure). 12) Callichroma opiparum, holotype male, dorsal habitus (By Jesus Santiago Moure)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5726544/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

